OL,3,CCall for public inquiry after police
OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,7,Fhas been urged to call a public
OL,8,Finquiry after revelations around
OL,9,Funlawful police surveillance of
OL,10,Fjournalists and lawyers.
OL,12,FJournalists Barry McCaffrey and Trevor
OL,13,FBirney were speaking after a report
OL,14,Frevealed police in the region
OL,15,Funlawfully used covert powers to
OL,16,Fattempt to uncover eight journalists'
OL,17,Fsources.
