OL,3,CCall for public inquiry after police
OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,FThe McCullough Review into
OL,7,Fsurveillance practices in the Police
OL,8,FService of Northern Ireland (PSNI)
OL,9,Falso found that attempts were made on
OL,10,F21 occasions to identify reporters'
OL,11,Fsources before 2015, and there were
OL,12,Ftwo instances of directed surveillance
OL,13,Fagainst an unnamed lawyer without
OL,14,Fproper authorisation.
OL,16,FTwo of the reporters targeted are
OL,17,FSharon O'Neill and Deborah McAleese
OL,18,Ffrom UTV.
