OL,6,FSharon O'Neill said: "This news is
OL,7,Freally disturbing and unnerving, for
OL,8,Fyears I've held the PSNI to account
OL,9,Fand also highlighted the good work
OL,10,Fthat goes on in communities.
OL,12,F"Now I find out that that same service
OL,13,Fhad been accessing phone to track down
OL,14,Fa source, and that feels like a total
OL,15,Fviolation."
OL,17,FDeborah McAleese was targeted when she
OL,18,Fwas the crime correspondent at the
OL,19,FBelfast Telegraph.
