OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,FAngus McCullough KC was commissioned
OL,7,Fby the PSNI to examine the issue after
OL,8,Fa tribunal last year ruled an
OL,9,Fundercover police operation to try to
OL,10,Funmask Mr McCaffrey and Mr Birnie's
OL,11,Fsources was unlawful.
OL,13,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,14,F(IPT) quashed a decision by former
OL,15,FPSNI chief constable Sir George
OL,16,FHamilton to approve a directed
OL,17,Fsurveillance authorisation (DSA) in an
OL,18,Finvestigation into the leaking of a
OL,19,Fconfidential document that appeared in
OL,20,Fa documentary made by the pair about a
OL,21,FTroubles massacre.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/32
