OL,3,CCall for public inquiry after police
OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,FThe tribunal also looked at
OL,7,Fallegations that the PSNI and the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police in London
OL,9,Funlawfully accessed Mr McCaffrey's
OL,10,Fphone data in unrelated operations in
OL,11,F2012 and 2013.
OL,13,FThe two forces conceded that those
OL,14,Foperations were unlawful.
OL,16,FSpeaking at a press conference in
OL,17,FBelfast on Wednesday, both men said a
OL,18,Fpublic inquiry is needed to reveal the
OL,19,Fextent of surveillance.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/32
