OL,3,CCall for public inquiry after police
OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,F"We have no faith that the PSNI are
OL,7,Fcapable of following the right road,
OL,8,Fwe believe that only a public inquiry
OL,9,Fwill force the PSNI to do the right
OL,10,Fthing," Mr McCaffrey said.
OL,12,F"It's not about us, it's about public
OL,13,Fconfidence, what has happened over the
OL,14,Fpast eight years with our case, with
OL,15,FVincent Kearney, Chris Moore, the
OL,16,Fconfidence in policing has been
OL,17,Fdestroyed, and it's not our fault.
OL,18,FIt's the fault of the PSNI and whoever
OL,19,Fwas allowing this to happen within the
OL,20,FPSNI.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]tD@AOU
