OL,3,CCall for public inquiry after police
OL,4,Csurveillance revelations
OL,6,F"We need to know who is pulling the
OL,7,Fstrings."
OL,9,FHe added: "There is one man who can
OL,10,Fsolve this. There is one man who can
OL,11,Finitiate a public inquiry, and that is
OL,12,FHilary Benn, and if he is really the
OL,13,FSecretary of State for Northern
OL,14,FIreland, and he cares for confidence
OL,15,Fin policing and the public, he will
OL,16,Finitiate a public inquiry because this
OL,17,Fcan't be allowed to go on."
