OL,6,FMr Birney said he wanted to remember
OL,7,Fthe families of the six people killed
OL,8,Fin Loughinisland in an attack by
OL,9,Floyalist paramilitaries, amid claims
OL,10,Fof security forces collusion, saying
OL,11,Fhe and Mr McCaffrey spent years
OL,12,Fsearching for truth and justice for
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"We remain committed to telling the
OL,16,Ftruth about what happened in
OL,17,FLoughinisland, and we will also
OL,18,Fcontinue to raise the alarm about
OL,19,Fpress freedom in Northern Ireland," he
OL,20,Fadded.
