OL,6,F"We welcome the work of Angus
OL,7,FMcCullough, we appreciate it, and we
OL,8,Fnow think it is a very important
OL,9,Fstepping stone, but only a stepping
OL,10,Fstone to a full public ventilation of
OL,11,Fthe facts around spying on
OL,12,Fjournalists."
