OL,6,FHe said the actions around journalists
OL,7,Fwere "well ventilated" on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fbut there is also concern around
OL,9,Fsurveillance of lawyers.
OL,11,F"That culture, for me, is something
OL,12,Fthat needs addressed," he said.
