OL,6,FMr McCullough said: "The report
OL,7,Fidentifies some specific cases in
OL,8,Fwhich I consider the covert measures
OL,9,Fare likely to have been authorised
OL,10,Funlawfully."
OL,12,FHe said the applications "appear to
